Class ReadRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • share.Request
      • share.ReadRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ReadRequest
extends Request
    The ReadRequest class represents reading from file requests. A ReadRequest object encapsulates all the information needed for a reading operation from file, whose name is set when the object is created.
    See Also:
    Request, Serialized Form
